{"tid":204570,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺POLY都可以行書院制","createTime":"2017-04-17T07:14:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-12T06:18:49.000Z","uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1fd537064d3b372a077ad443f20197460006c56c","tid":204570,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T07:14:37.000Z","msg":"每個CORE=一個書院<br />\nA書院<br />\nB書院<br />\nC書院<br />\n.........<br />\nZ書院<br />\n<br />\n所有理大全日制本科生都可選擇一所書院，成為該院的一分子。每所書院都是獨樹一幟的，有各自的文化，但匯聚在一起，卻塑造了理工大學的精神面貌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n書院培養師生的歸屬感，提供機會給學生表達個別的興趣。書院亦建立校友網絡及提供有關經濟援助。"},{"pid":"461bfecac54f6a3fc2a1d0e1dce3786c0c13aea9","tid":204570,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T07:20:08.000Z","msg":"書院制好無謂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：讀過書院制unj"},{"pid":"95bafaf1ef7cd212588b695e37c0abc51ac60098","tid":204570,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T08:18:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>書院制好無謂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：讀過書院制unj</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為書院而識多D人,唔好咩"},{"pid":"ba4f4fdc68a489e200986c4ec5f1634e47b61bcc","tid":204570,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T08:25:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>書院制好無謂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：讀過書院制unj</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為書院而識多D人,唔好咩</blockquote><br />\n你走讀生既話，其實有無書院無分別"},{"pid":"766469c78e9eefbbc3e6814d784f178a8fa632fd","tid":204570,"uid":114294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:38:56.000Z","msg":"Facility 點分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaa8ee955047c48cee874dba93971527318f4fdb","tid":204570,"uid":25260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:41:04.000Z","msg":"Poly<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d60e14d028d072322b24b1aa1024b478486f944","tid":204570,"uid":52685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14: